# Build context for the single-container image (Dockerfile at the repo root,
# used by Railway/Render). frontend/.dockerignore does NOT apply here — that one
# only takes effect when the build context is frontend/ (docker-compose).
#
# Dependencies are installed inside each build stage. Copying a host node_modules
# over that install pastes platform-native binaries into an Alpine image
# (@next/swc-win32-x64-msvc, @next/swc-darwin-arm64) and `next build` fails.
node_modules
**/node_modules
.next
**/.next
**/__pycache__
**/.venv

# Never ship secrets into a build context.
.env
**/.env
!**/.env.example

.git
.gitignore
docs/
